ğŸ“ EduRisk AI â€“ Backend API

A FastAPI backend service that serves a trained machine learning model to predict student academic outcomes and dropout risk.

This API powers the EduRisk AI Early Warning System, enabling real-time prediction for:

ğŸ¯ Predicted Outcome: Dropout / Enrolled / Graduate

ğŸ“Š Dropout Risk Score (0â€“100%)

ğŸ” Confidence Score

ğŸ“ˆ Probability distribution across all classes

ğŸ“‚ Batch CSV processing

ğŸš€ Overview

This backend exposes two main endpoints:

Endpoint	Method	Description
/predict	POST	Predict outcome for a single student
/predict_csv	POST	Upload CSV file and receive predictions file

The API loads a trained multi-class XGBoost model saved as:

student_success_multiclass.pkl
