ğŸ”¹ POST /predict_csv

Upload CSV file and receive predictions CSV in return.

Request

multipart/form-data

File field name: file

Response

Returns CSV file including additional columns:

prediction

confidence

dropout_risk_score

prob_dropout

prob_enrolled

prob_graduate

